Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.75,0:21:50.25,EDlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}INSIDE  IDENTITY
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.25,0:21:53.05,EDlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}我的棲身之地在哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.18,0:22:05.69,EDlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}誤解令人感到害羞什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.77,0:22:08.27,EDlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}率真令人難以忍受什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.40,0:22:10.61,EDlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}無論他人怎麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.61,0:22:13.49,EDlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}我也不知到底「正確」為何物
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.53,0:22:16.11,EDlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}強迫自己去習慣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.32,0:22:18.70,EDlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}一成不變的日常
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.74,0:22:21.45,EDlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}將沉淪的種種個性
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.54,0:22:23.66,EDlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}啃食飲盡  唾棄嘲笑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.70,0:22:28.29,EDlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}希望你能理解這樣的我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.38,0:22:33.63,EDlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}欲言又止
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.71,0:22:38.59,EDlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}連思考「為什麼誰都無法理解我」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.72,0:22:43.68,EDlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}都已成為一種奢侈了嗎？了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.89,0:22:48.98,EDlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}多愁善感的太陽
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.06,0:22:51.69,EDlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}釋放出過多的熱量
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.77,0:22:54.11,EDlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}把我曬得快不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.23,0:22:59.20,EDlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}按耐不住吶喊的衝動
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.36,0:23:05.20,EDlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}不顧一切地渴求IDENTITY
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.20,0:23:07.66,EDlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}INSIDE  MY  FEELING
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.75,0:23:10.25,EDlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}INSIDE  MY  JUSTICE
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.29,0:23:12.79,EDlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}千萬別妨礙我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.88,0:23:14.84,EDlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}我的棲身之地在哪裡？
